commonPatterns:
Encapsulation with validation:
class BankAccount {
  private double bal;
  public BankAccount(double init){ bal = Math.max(0, init); }
  public void deposit(double a){ if(a>0) bal+=a; }
  public boolean withdraw(double a){ if(a>0 && a<=bal){ bal-=a; return true; } return false; }
}

Immutable value object:
final class Point2D {
  private final int x, y;
  public Point2D(int x, int y){ this.x=x; this.y=y; }
  public int getX(){ return x; } public int getY(){ return y; }
}

Polymorphic processing:
List<Shape> shapes = List.of(new Circle(2), new Rectangle(3,4));
double sum=0; for(Shape s:shapes) sum+=s.area();

Delegation via composition:
class StopWatch { long start; void tic(){ start=System.nanoTime(); } long toc(){ return System.nanoTime()-start; } }
class Sorter { private final StopWatch sw = new StopWatch(); void sort(int[] a){ sw.tic(); /* ... */ long t=sw.toc(); } }

